<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l2">ʒu Graıcʒ . vnd <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan> ʒu Pernaw . Vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
