<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l4">Edler lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns . als vns eẅr edel vnd <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l5"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawffleẅt vnd furleẅt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . wıe dıe ander </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l7"><expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> faren vnd <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . denn dıe <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> ſtraſſen etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l8"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etwıeuıl <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawffleẅt vnd <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . dıe auf dıſʒ ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l9">anheim ſein dıe dıe <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> maıſt pawen . für vns beſant vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l10">ʒu rede geſacʒt / Dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> daʒ ſıe ſölıch <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> lıeber füren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l11">denn <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . ſo ſein aber Jr etlıch auf <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſwerlıch be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l12">ſchedıgt vnd Jn ır hab vnd gut in dem geleyt <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l13">ſo nemen ſıe von <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> notdurft vnfrıds vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſölıch <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l14">fürſıch ʒe faren vnd ʒu <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> da Jn ır hab vnd gut ſıcher geleytet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l15"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> vnd hin <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> mug . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo getrawen wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l16"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol . daʒ Jr dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> auf ſölıch <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> niht nötgen Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l17">Jn vnd <expan>ır<ex>er</ex></expan> hab . <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchaden ʒuʒıehen wellet . wan wır <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan> Jr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteet</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l18">ſelbs wol . daʒ das niht <expan>bıllıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb eẅr edel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l19">vnd <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> . etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Edıgij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="108v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rewssen von Plawen dem
                                <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                        Graicz und <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Pernaw, und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Parsp<ex>er</ex>g,</expan>
<expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Waldeck
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler, lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> und lieber <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
            Hanns, als uns ewr edel und <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawfflewt und
            furlewt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie die ander <expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan>
            faren und <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> denn die <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
            strassen etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
              <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etwievil
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawfflewt und <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, die auf
            disz zeit anheim sein, die die <expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> maist pawen, für uns besant und
              <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede gesaczt; die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz sie sölich <expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan>
            lieber füren denn <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan>, so sein aber ir etlich auf
              <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan> swerlich beschedigt und in ir hab und gut in dem geleyt
                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so nemen sie von
                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> notdurft, unfrids und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
            sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> sölich <expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan> fürsich ze
            faren und zu <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> da in ir hab und gut sicher geleytet
                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und hin <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> mug.
                <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so getrawen wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell
            und <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol, daz ir die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> auf sölich <expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan> niht nötgen
            und in und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> schaden
            zuziehen wellet, wan wir <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan>, ir
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steet</expan> selbs wol, daz das niht
              <expan>billich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr edel und
                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Edigii. </ab>
</div>
